CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 28, 1963, pg. 13, reads: "Mother - Daughter Team - Abstract patterns created in glass mark this unusual floor lamp, created by Pittsburgh artist and designer Murrel Wynn Jones (right), who specializes in that medium.  Often working with her is daughter Barbara Eve (left), an international traveler, as well as an artist in her own right. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Barbara Eve and Murrel Wynn Jones standing on either side of glass floor lamp
